    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，INIT到HANDSHAKING的转换已标注on_connected(FleetManagement)。接下来握手完成后如何进入数据传输？",
